data.description: Welcome to your new Chubbuck home! This beautiful home is just bursting with space and charm. This split entry home is sure to not disappoint. Wether you're looking for spacious living, or an investor looking for a home with two... yes TWO full kitchens you have found what you are looking for. This home also sits on a massive 0.31 acre lot with an enormous back yard for entertaining. The possibilities are endless. You will also enjoy just sitting and relaxing in your own private sun room. If you are looking for homeownership that could also host a roommate look no further. You found it! Do not miss your chance to own this home. Set up a showing today!!
